author: Joseph Wulfsohn
title: Bill Maher, 'World War Z' author agree China would 'shut down' coronavirus rumors
description: "Real Time" host Bill Maher raised questions about the origins of the coronavirus pandemic, pointing to the "rumors" that the virus could have been developed in a Chinese laboratory.
